<paragraph blockId="65.[151,1437,151,392]" pageId="65" pageNumber="66">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,330,151,176]" pageId="65" pageNumber="66">Bionomics.</emphasis>
Adults fly in April. Otherwise biology unknown. The 
<typeStatus box="[972,1070,151,176]" pageId="65" pageNumber="66">holotype</typeStatus>
was swept from the vegetation during early afternoon between light snow flurries.
</paragraph>
